---
title: Cheesy Lentil and Beyond Meat® Nachos with Lime Crema and Guac
description: Lentil 'nachos' are a quirky-fun combination of loaded tortillas scattered with all the classic toppings! Crisp seasoned nachos are topped with Beyond Meat®, mozzarella cheese, Mexican-spiced lentils and lime crema.
